widgets_values: A luxurious, deep emerald green velvet couch, ornately tufted with large buttons.  It sits in a warmly lit living room decorated for Christmas, with a roaring fire in the fireplace behind it.  Soft, golden fairy lights are draped across the mantelpiece and twinkle against the dark wood.  A plush, red throw blanket is casually draped over one arm of the couch, and a stack of brightly wrapped presents sits on the floor in front of it.  A sprig of holly rests on the top present.  The overall atmosphere is cozy and inviting, suggesting a comfortable Christmas Eve gathering.  Render in a photorealistic style with cinematic lighting.
